all of them at once!

455
00:27:03.640 --> 00:27:05.770
I'm gonna go help them!

456
00:27:05.770 --> 00:27:07.150
O-Okay!

457
00:27:07.150 --> 00:27:09.020
I'll stay here...

458
00:27:09.020 --> 00:27:10.610
and... hold down the fort!

459
00:27:10.610 --> 00:27:14.450
I can't believe Moss Head is about to die
when we're so close to the One Piece...

460
00:27:14.450 --> 00:27:17.120
You're going, too! Our crew is in danger!

461
00:27:18.870 --> 00:27:22.580
For Master Nami... I'll get going!

462
00:27:22.950 --> 00:27:28.330
